des:
ezhome can control different types of smart devices via voice commands, such as lamps, switches, sockets, curtains, and etc.
Simple device, simplify your life.

After connecting Alexa to your ezhome Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "ezhome" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register a new account in the "ezhome" app (or log in if you’re already registered);
(3). Connect the ezhome smart devices and use the “ezhome” app to configure them;
(4). In our "ezhome" app change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "ezhome" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "ezhome" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "ezhome", and you'll be navigated to login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now the setup is finished. You can interact with the skill using the commands described above.
